Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:05.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Deduction flows with the rhythm of the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.62,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and causes alibi tricks to fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.34,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko's world of Karuizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After all, there's trouble with a spicy case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:14.91,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.91,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're running late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, old man, it's nothing to get heated up over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Why the heck do I, Kogoro Mouri, have to serve as a driver for two brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're from the Suzuki Financial Group, don't you have your own chauffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! I don't want a chauffer driving me around on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate feeling like I'm being watched!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there's one kid who's got a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so be careful you don't catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It took me a while to get Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be okay, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a cold, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, just fine. I just got the sniffles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, now that we're all set, off we go to Karuizawa! All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:59.37,Title,,0,0,0,,Suspicious Spicy Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:59.37,Title,,0,0,0,,(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, but If you start feeling bad, tell me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, with that cold, why didn't you just stay home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager at Poirot offered to watch you for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want to go to Karuizawa to see Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s villa too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And besides, if I know Sonoko for who she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:36.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}she'll probably think up some no good plan like always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We'll do just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll get a really good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? We're going to play tennis to get guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! Around this time, the tennis courts near our villa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are full of college students!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, if you do something like that, Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will get mad at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s the only guy for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's going to get someone today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll use a tennis outfit to show off your body and wow a guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then you'll take a photo with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and send it as an e-mail attachment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll do all this to get that boyfriend of yours, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think Shin'ichi will get jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:22.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew she was up to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Besides, the only thing I have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is a track suit from Teitan High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have tennis wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought you tennis wear and brought it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tada! Super mini, and cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}S-Short!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! I could never wear something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring spats with me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess there's no choice then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll just have to wear your plain panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:03.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}P-Plain panties?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damnit! I'd love to see that, but not if other people see it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't know what you guys are up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but if my daughter is embarrassing herself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for that detective brat, I'm turning around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there will be lots of university babes there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,University babes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so nice in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Where are all my university babes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we can't play tennis then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't know if I should feel happy or sad over this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, I was looking forward to seeing Ran's panty flash shots that I hadn't seen in a while today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:57.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, I guess it's for the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Somebody's on the tennis court...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could they be, a university babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:21.28,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiroto Akashi (32)\NTennis Instructor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:21.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was just recalling memories of when I first met my wife here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's already taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you guys came to play tennis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would you like me to coach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a tennis instructor, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My house is nearby, so if you're interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the offer, but I'm afraid we're busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, so we couldn't catch any men after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,let's catch some fish instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey, what's with this turn of events?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just you wait! I'll catch us some delicious fish for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the villa, the cook and my big sister are waiting with dinner already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't the river water rising?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, the fish took my bait and tackle off again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because you don't tie it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fish lines are smooth, so unless you tie them like this—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Your rod, it's being pulled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, I must have hooked a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?! That's my rental car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been washed into the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Didn't I tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:55.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}you parked the car too close to the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damnit! I'm not letting the river take the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just give up, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, but my right wrist hurts a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you sprained it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably landed on it when you fell into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's way better than being stranded in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is no time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of our things were in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our cell phones are all out of range,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's getting dark after all of this walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you think we might be lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! You mean you've been walking around not knowing where we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I've just been following my intuition...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:09:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? There's a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You mean people are living out in the mountains like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the mountains? It must be a mountain witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's have her take us in for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to get a change of clothes for this brat, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Sorry to intrude at this hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is anybody home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You guys are the ones who are monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:40.89,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hiroto's Father
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,So are you guys more solicitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you brought kids, you can't trick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. We're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go home! Go home!\NThis is no place for swindlers like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a funny story!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys fell into the river while trying to fish out your car that drifted into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a laughing matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. But he'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this sling, and a splint to fix his wrist in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'll recover in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, please turn this way and let me look inside your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your throat is red and your voice is getting hoarse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so try to avoid using your voice too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you might get acute laryngitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sound like you're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I used to be a personal trainer and a coach for a pro,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I learned a lot from when I did that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyways, how do the clothes from my childhood fit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they the right size?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They fit perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I smell curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's just leftovers from last night though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By any chance, do you guys want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is delicious! Restaurant quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of your sore throat Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you get eggs over rice, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like the spiciness of this curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife must be a good cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who made this was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife passed away 3 years ago today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why you were at the tennis court recalling memories of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, back when I was a trainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made healthy meals for my players, focusing on nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I was a better cook than my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to go take some curry to my father upstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so help yourselves to seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, I brought you some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sure is taking his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already been 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This long pull string hanging from the light above!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It keeps getting in the way of me eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining! You've already had two plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That string is for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted a string he could reach with his hunched back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you sure took a long time, considering all you did was give him curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my father started saying some strange things, so we started talking to each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm not going to eat because I want to die."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:13:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since his wife and his daughter-in-law died before him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he thinks that he has a curse placed on him by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he seems to be fine now that he got some curry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since it's his favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The road is blocked due to a landslide,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you can't come pick us up today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, you can stay here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got some spare futons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you go get my father's dish for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, keep in mind, he's a slow eater and can be uncooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If his light is still on, he's still eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so just come back down quietly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The room's light is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Quietly, quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a stance for a forehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He must be done eating by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go back up to get his dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll go up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:34.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Quietly, quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, the light is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? He's not on his futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's bleeding from his mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still warm, but his toes are starting to stiffen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I estimate that he's been dead for around 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but can you call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:16:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess the Gunma police officers will be coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, the Gunma officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been summoned so here I am, ta-daaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For you Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I would go through fire and water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain may have blocked the roads, but when you called I came immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Does the Gunma Police Station have nobody else to dispatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? What kind of murder case is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the weapon? Any evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to do it, right?\NThe Sleeping Kogoro deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop smiling all over the place here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have some prudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, we're don't even know if this is a murder case yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the body over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased is the owner of this house, Iwao Akashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body was discovered by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:17:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my daughter Ran, who came to clear his curry dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she found him, the room's light was turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when she checked hour and a half earlier, the light was on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she thought he was still eating his curry and didn't enter the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I checked immediately after the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he seemed to have been dead for about 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were four of us in the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we were all in the living room downstairs for at least 2 hours, so we all have alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I wasn't in the living room then, because I was taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That means, the one who committed the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would be you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, the first time I came to this house was today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where the rope is kept, so I couldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a bit concerning that the victim is bleeding from his mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but since this is obviously a suicide—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What makes it concerning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought people who die like this always bleed from their mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:03.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I've seen it all the time in movies and on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A doctor told me once that when something is wrapped around your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your face gets swollen due to the blood circulation stopping, so you don't bleed from the mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,unless the inside is cut or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So in movies and on TV, I think they do it to make it visually obvious that the person is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, don't try to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll strain your throat with your cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if it's as the boy said,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he's bleeding from his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's due to him going to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he went to go to the dentist about a hurting cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I ask who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Iwao Akashi's son, Hiroto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He adopted me when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His right molar has been pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that after he died,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it bled from here, causing blood to come out when he drooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you know when and where your father went to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No... he went to it by himself two or three days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already know this is definitely suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably used this stepladder here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got on here and pulled the rope around the thick beam there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt this is suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to what Hiroto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his father was saying that he wanted to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will I do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told everybody at the station I was going to videotape Sleeping Kogoro's deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will I tell everyone when I get back to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's a suicide, you don't have to bother with investigating further.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old man is bent over and only about 30 centimeters taller than me, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the string for the light here is made to fit the old man's height,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't reach it even if I stretch my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kid is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means this isn't a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, a while back when my father got up late at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the string got in his face and he hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the light pull string in my father's room is short.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it is suicide after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be waiting downstairs in the living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so call me if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Getting all of you dragged into something like this while on your vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you like fishing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This book, "Fishing for Beginners".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, my wife was the one bought that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife who passed away of illness 3 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I never saw her go fishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so maybe she was planning on doing so after she recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something's strange about this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:31.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The way he made Ran go all the way upstairs for the dish,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:35.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the length of the light's pull string,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:38.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the story about him going to the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:41.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he knew that he got his teeth treated 2 or 3 days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:45.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}why did he make something like curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If when he was a trainer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:51.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he made food and focused on nutrition,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:54.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he should have noticed that detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:56.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the curry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:59.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he made far too much for just the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:03.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He couldn't have known beforehand that we would come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:05.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:08.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the knot tied on the pull string.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:10.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No question...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:15.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This case... has something fishy behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but when I went in front of the room the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the old man weeping "Uuugh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:24:00.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I get the picture... of this trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:03.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay, now that I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:08.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:11.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I lost my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:17.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,Suspicious Spicy Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:17.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,(Part 2)
